	Nonfunctional domains:

		- subscribe.theepochtimes.com	(times out)


	Problematic domains:

		- ad.epochtimes.com
			- CN: yet8.acosm.com

		- (www.)theepochtimes.com
			- CN: Epoch Times
			- At least some pages redirect to http


